Write a java program to print below pattern:
-----*****
-----*   *
-----*   *        [- means spaces]
-----*   *
-----*****

taking the user input as number 
taking the user input as character to be printed
taking for loop for rows
taking inner for loop for printing spaces in pattern(j<=n)
taking one more loop for printing the starts and spaces in this spaces 
and starts will be printed based on if condition(i==1,5 & j==1,5)
outer for loop for  printing the next line